{"id":10780,"date":"2024-03-09T16:29:15","date_gmt":"2024-03-09T09:29:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10780"},"modified":"2024-03-09T16:29:47","modified_gmt":"2024-03-09T09:29:47","slug":"cach-tinh-dien-tich-san","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san\/","title":{"rendered":"Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eafm r\u00f5 khi mua nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf. V\u1eady di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? <\/span><b>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng chung c\u01b0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vinhomeland<\/a><\/strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n, hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng trong m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh nh\u00e0 \u1edf (g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u1ea7ng m\u00e1i, h\u00e0nh lang, ban c\u00f4ng, s\u00e0n t\u1ea7ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ea7ng tum, t\u1ea7ng n\u1eeda h\u1ea7m, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m\u2026).<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng chung c\u01b0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, g\u1ed3m: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ban c\u00f4ng g\u1eafn v\u1edbi logia. Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi nhau.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c xin c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p thi c\u00f4ng. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 khi b\u00e0n giao c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10781\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10781\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10781 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-1.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/500;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10781\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10781\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-1.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong thi c\u00f4ng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a s\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. N\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng bao b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n nh\u01b0 logia, h\u00e0nh lang, gi\u1ebfng tr\u1eddi, ban c\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u thang, c\u00e1c h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3)&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1eady t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch c\u1ed9ng t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, ph\u1ea1m vi bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 t\u1ea7ng tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m. T\u1ea7ng \u00e1p m\u00e1i, hi\u00ean nh\u00e0, s\u00e2n ph\u01a1i, nh\u00e0 kho\u2026 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i s\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh v\u00e0o t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a k\u1ef9 s\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t m\u00e0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u00e0:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng = Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng + C\u00e1c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c \u0111i k\u00e8m (ph\u1ea7n n\u1ec1n m\u00f3ng, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m, s\u00e2n, m\u00e1i \u2026)\u00a0<\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng chung c\u01b0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf, c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y = (di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n \u1edf + di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n v\u00e1ch + ban c\u00f4ng, logia) &#8211; (di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh + di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n c\u00e1ch c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 + di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ed9p k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch tim t\u01b0\u1eddng = Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u1edf + Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u0103n v\u00e1ch + ban c\u00f4ng, logia.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ta d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean, gia ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10782\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10782\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10782 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-2.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/500;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10782\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10782\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-2.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10782\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5ng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00ean trong ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1eddng bao b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea1m vi c\u00f3 m\u00e1i che. Ngo\u00e0i ra ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f2n bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n l\u1ee3p m\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 tr\u1ea7n, s\u00e0n b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u thang l\u1ed9 thi\u00ean\u2026 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 100%.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh c\u00e1c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111i k\u00e8m<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7u hay \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u0111i k\u00e8m trong m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng bao g\u1ed3m s\u00e2n b\u00e3i, m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0, b\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1t, b\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ea7m\u2026 l\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4. Tuy nhi\u00ean khu v\u1ef1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh l\u00e0 100% nh\u01b0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh ri\u00eang di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u gia ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y theo d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o: m\u00f3ng b\u00e8, m\u00f3ng c\u1ecdc hay m\u00f3ng \u0111\u01a1n. M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i m\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Lo\u1ea1i m\u00f3ng \u0111\u01a1n: 20 &#8211; 25% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ea7ng 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Lo\u1ea1i m\u00f3ng \u0111\u01a1n: 30 &#8211; 40% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ea7ng 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Lo\u1ea1i m\u00f3ng \u0111\u01a1n: 40 &#8211; 60% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ea7ng 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p ho\u1eb7c n\u1ec1n c\u00f3 d\u1ea7m, ph\u1ea7n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh theo t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 20 &#8211; 25% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n t\u1ea7ng 1 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gia ch\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 gia c\u1ed1 th\u00eam n\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c n\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7n tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh kh\u00e1c theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 quan c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea7m ng\u1ea7m<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd quy \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea7m ng\u1ea7m theo \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201ccode v\u1ec9a h\u00e8\u201d c\u1ee7a con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01a1i m\u00e0 ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.\u00a0 C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb \u201ccode \u0111\u1ec9nh ram h\u1ea7m\u201d trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy t\u1eafc quy \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec7n t\u00edch h\u1ea7m ng\u1ea7m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 1.5m, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 150% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u t\u1eeb 1.5 &#8211; 2m, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 170% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 2m, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 200% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khi t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 l\u00e1t g\u1ea1ch n\u1ec1n, t\u01b0\u1eddng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 xung quanh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chu\u1ea9n an to\u00e0n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cho c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy t\u1eafc t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 20m2, ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 100% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 40m2, ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 70% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u00e2n tr\u00ean 40m2, ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 50% t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i k\u00e8m n\u1ebfu c\u00f3<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i k\u00e8m c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0, sau khi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 th\u00ec gia ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ecdn c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c quy \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. C\u00e1c c\u00e1ch quy \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 50% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng ng\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 khung s\u1eaft c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 60% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p c\u00f3 l\u00e1t ng\u00f3i: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 85% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p l\u00e1t g\u1ea1ch: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 10% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 50% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng t\u00f4n: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 30% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i ng\u00f3i b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ed1t th\u00e9p: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 100% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 x\u00e2y bao quanh: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 15%\u00a0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i ch\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 x\u00e2y bao quanh: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 30-50%\u00a0 t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u00e1i tr\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng th\u1ea1ch cao: c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 25% v\u00e0o di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 chung<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111i k\u00e8m, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u01b0 sau:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e1i che: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 50% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n t\u1ea7ng d\u01b0\u1edbi<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u00e1i che: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 75% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n t\u1ea7ng d\u01b0\u1edbi<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 m\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 lam s\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ban c\u00f4ng, gi\u00e0n b\u00ea t\u00f4ng, trang tr\u00ed, t\u01b0\u1eddng bao tr\u00ean 1m: di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 100% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh t\u1eeb 1m v\u00e0 n\u1ec1n nh\u00e0 t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng 50% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10783\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10783\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10783 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-3.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/550;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10783\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10783\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-3.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10783\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u khu v\u1ef1c trong c\u0103n nh\u00e0<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hai kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhau b\u1edfi n\u00f3 kh\u00e1 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1eabn nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y V<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">inhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">L\u00e0 t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng (t\u1ea7ng m\u00e1i, t\u1ea7ng tum, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m, s\u00e0n t\u1ea7ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt\u2026), h\u00e0nh lang v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh v\u00e0o di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n m\u1eb7t s\u00e0n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, t\u00ednh t\u1eeb m\u00e9p t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e9p t\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean kia.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c t\u00ednh\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00e1c s\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng + Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u00e1i, t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m, ban c\u00f4ng, m\u00f3ng nh\u00e0. s\u00e2n\u2026)<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">B\u1eb1ng t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t sau:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">* Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n t\u1eebng t\u1ea7ng = 100% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00e1i t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u00f3\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">* Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u00f3ng = 50 &#8211; 75% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch 1 s\u00e0n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">* Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch b\u1ec3 n\u01b0\u1edbc = 60 &#8211; 70% di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng 1 s\u00e0n\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">(t\u00ednh theo \u0111\u01a1n gi\u00e1 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng)<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c gi\u00e1 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, tr\u00e1nh ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh cho gia ch\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch th\u00f4ng th\u1ee7y, tim t\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch \u1edf. Bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp khi c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh thi c\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 sau khi b\u00e0n giao nh\u00e0 th\u00f4.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div id=\"attachment_10784\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10784\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10784 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-4.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/550;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10784\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10784\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san-4.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n\" width=\"800\" height=\"550\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10784\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n gi\u1ed1ng nhau<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0, gia ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap t\u00ednh to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed l\u00e0m nh\u00e0, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u00f3 c\u00f2n li\u00ean quan tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn quy ho\u1ea1ch, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a V<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">inhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/cach-tinh-dien-tich-san\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;10780&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh di\u1ec7n t\u00edch s\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({co